      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Continuum elastoplastic constitutive model with isotropic hardening justified by literature for Ti-6Al-4V at quasi-static rates; contact formulation validated against known analytical solutions.",
      "rationale": "Bilinear isotropic hardening plasticity model for Ti-6Al-4V calibrated from tensile coupon data (n=5 coupons, same material lot). Penalty contact with friction coefficient 0.3 consistent with Ti-on-Ti literature. Model form appropriate for quasi-static compression-bending at room temperature. Achieved level 3 meets required level 3."
    },
    {
