      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties from same lot as test specimens; geometry from certified metrology report; uncertainty in key inputs propagated via Monte Carlo (n=1000 samples).",
      "rationale": "Elastic modulus 114 GPa, yield strength 880 MPa, ultimate strength 950 MPa from tensile coupon testing of same Ti-6Al-4V lot. Geometry from CMM report with tolerances ±0.01 mm. Monte Carlo uncertainty propagation (n=1000) shows QoI sensitivity to material variability within 3.5% band. Achieved level 3 meets required level 3."
