      "rationale": "N=11 constructs (6 at Lab 1, 5 at Lab 2) assembled from production-representative pedicle screws and UHMWPE test blocks per ASTM F1717. Dimensional inspection of all screws confirms within ±0.02 mm of nominal. Material certifications for Ti-6Al-4V and UHMWPE on file. Achieved level 3 meets required level 3."
