      "rationale": "Construct stiffness and yield force are the primary performance metrics cited in FDA guidance for pedicle screw 510(k) submissions. Force at 40 mm displacement provides secondary safety margin indicator. All three QoIs are directly interpretable in the clinical context of spinal fixation construct performance. Achieved level 3 meets required level 3."
